          <div class="inline-flex items-center bg-mint-100 text-mint-800 px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-semibold mb-4">
            <span>2025 E-Commerce Trends</span>
          </div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
            Modern Design Trends We Implement
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
